---
---

<section class="pull">
	<div class="wrap pull-grid">
		<svg class="open-q" viewBox="0 0 80 80" aria-hidden="true">
			<text x="0" y="62" font-family="Gilroy, sans-serif" font-weight="900" font-size="84" fill="var(--orange)">"</text>
		</svg>

		<blockquote class="pull-quote reveal">
			<p>
				Collaborating with Martin's team has been nothing short of
				exceptional. Their creativity knows no bounds, and every
				deliverable consistently exceeds expectations.
				<span class="punch">Trust me — you'll wish you found them sooner.</span>
			</p>
			<footer>
				<div class="who">— Aber Weiss</div>
			</footer>
		</blockquote>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.pull {
		padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 130px) 0;
		background: var(--teal-ink);
		color: var(--paper);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.pull::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse at 80% 20%,
			rgba(252, 182, 38, 0.18) 0%,
			transparent 50%
		),
		radial-gradient(
			ellipse at 20% 80%,
			rgba(20, 124, 145, 0.4) 0%,
			transparent 55%
		);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.pull-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
		gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 48px);
		align-items: start;
		max-width: 1080px;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.open-q {
		width: 80px;
		height: 80px;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.pull-quote {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.pull-quote p {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: clamp(24px, 3.4vw, 48px);
		line-height: 1.18;
		letter-spacing: -0.022em;
		margin: 0 0 32px;
		color: var(--paper);
	}
	.pull-quote .hl {
		color: var(--gold);
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	.pull-quote .punch {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 12px;
		color: var(--orange);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.pull-quote footer {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2px;
		padding-top: 20px;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
	}
	.who {
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: var(--paper);
	}
	.role {
		font-size: 0.86rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.pull-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.open-q { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
	}
</style>
